      "content": "but that's just what people say to make themselves feel better. in reality, the wreckage is still there. everyone is going to see me as this person who just failed and lost everything, and there's no way to undo that. sometimes i just think about how much easier it would be if the story just ended here, instead of having to drag this failure around for the rest of my life. it seems like the only way to actually stop the shame is to just not be here.",
